room_title: Escape room "The Hideout" by Arcane Escape Rooms in Los Angeles
room_description:
Fear has become rampant in this dystopian society as citizens continue to be captured and destroyed by The Agency. Now your brother has been taken. Although you fear the worst, you have a desperate hope that he may have escaped, and you continue to search for any sign of where he may be hiding.
While running from Agency Collectors, you and your friends have stumbled upon a clue that reignites your hope of finding your brother alive. You are the only one who can decipher your brotherâ€™s clues and follow him to safety. Can you escape into the secret passageway before you are found, captured and destroyed?
